This paper focuses on the Quality of Experience (QoE) of mobile networks, which is closely related to the field of network infrastructure (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the impact of network speed on QoE, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of smartphone applications, which can be classified under information theory (cs.IT) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
